rComments: Great prof - he really cares about his students and wants you to do well in his class. He will use both the textbook and stuff he says in class on his quizzes and exams. You really need to understand the course material in order to do well on his long answer questions.

Bon professeur, le début peut être difficile a bien assimiler, quiz presque chaque semaine, mais a la fin de la session ça  a valu la peine, on est bien prépare pour lexam final. Mais le projet de session était intéressant mais TRES long. Good Luck :)
